17:08.161 --> 17:09.629
Oh, no, no, no.

17:09.662 --> 17:11.298
I know that, Robin.

17:11.331 --> 17:13.100
It's not that. You're fine.

17:13.133 --> 17:16.069
I just... I wanted
to give us a break

17:16.103 --> 17:17.670
