pressure off,

17:17.704 --> 17:20.207
because, you know,

17:20.240 --> 17:22.209
if-if I get a room
and you get a room,

17:22.242 --> 17:24.477
then we could both do
whatever we want.

17:24.511 --> 17:28.348
If we only have one room,
then we can only do one thing.

17:28.381 --> 17:31.151
Do you know what
I'm saying, buddy?

17:31.184 --> 17:32.619
(chuckles nervously)

17:34.254 --> 17:37.056
Oh, my God. I'm not trying
to make things awkward,

17:37.090 --> 17:38.425
I'm really not, I just...

17:38.458 --> 17:39.992
was hoping that...

17:40.026 --> 17:42.162
