that I had to ask, so...
Ah.

17:49.636 --> 17:52.472
um...
Okay, okay. Wow.
(chuckles)

17:52.505 --> 17:56.509
Now, I planned this trip
very carefully, and...

17:56.543 --> 17:58.111
I was excited to...

17:58.145 --> 18:00.880
