every stage of it.

18:00.913 --> 18:03.116
So...

18:03.150 --> 18:05.985
this is a bit of an ice pack
to my balls...

18:06.018 --> 18:07.554
to tell you the truth.

18:09.088 --> 18:11.624
Oh.

18:11.658 --> 18:14.161
Well, I didn't mean
to ice-pack your balls.

18:14.194 --> 18:16.696
I was just trying...
No, it's okay.
It's okay.

18:19.299 --> 18:21.401
Okay.

18:21.434 --> 18:23.536
We're staying
at the Redwood Inn.

18:23.570 --> 18:24.604
Okay. Thanks.

18:24.637 --> 18:26.706
And I will call...

18:26.739 --> 18:29.376
I will book you a separate room.

18:30.410 --> 18:31.711
Thanks.

18:31.744 --> 18:33.446
I'm going to the bathroom.

18:33.480 --> 18:34.881
Oh. Yeah.

18:34.914 --> 18:36.783
It's okay.

18:42.655 --> 18:43.923
Mm.

18:46.259 --> 18:47.894
(exhales)

18:50.597 --> 18:52.432
That's fun stuff.

18:52.465 --> 18:54.767
Mm-hmm.

18:54.801 --> 18:56.269
Mmm.

18:59.706 --> 19:02.942
That's a bit of an ice pack
to my balls.

19:02.975 --> 19:04.511
Mm.

