I'm pretty hungry.

19:12.151 --> 19:15.955
I'm excited about
eating food and stuff.

19:15.988 --> 19:18.458
(groans):
Oh. It's, like...

19:18.491 --> 19:21.294
sometimes my levels of...

19:21.328 --> 19:23.930
(clicks tongue)
not having food in my body

19:23.963 --> 19:26.999
just get to a low point.

