For the hotel thing.

21:01.594 --> 21:03.162
Oh. No, no, no.

21:03.195 --> 21:04.731
Robin, it's okay.

21:04.764 --> 21:07.600
No, no, it's not okay.

21:07.634 --> 21:09.736
It's really shitty of me.

21:09.769 --> 21:13.506
I mean, I've been thinking
about this all this time,

21:13.540 --> 21:16.443
