21:22.982 --> 21:25.217
I don't know, Sam.

21:25.251 --> 21:27.554
I'm really sorry.

21:27.587 --> 21:30.089
(sighs)
I-I'm so dumb.

21:30.122 --> 21:32.291
You were really
